description: This Alexa skill will take a dollar and/or cent value and determine how much that money would weigh in US currency. Bills are assumed to be 1g and coin weights vary from 2g to 11g. The skill will determine the fewest number of bills and coins to get the weight.
name: Money Weight
shortDescription: Tell Alexa a dollar amount (with or without cents) and she will tell you how much it would weigh in grams and pounds.
